hoenn_pokedex.name: Treecko
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has small hooks on the bottom of its feet that enable it to scale vertical walls. It coolly stares down foes.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Grovyle
hoenn_pokedex.description: It lives in dense jungles. While closing in on its prey, it leaps from branch to branch.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Sceptile
hoenn_pokedex.description: The leaves that grow on its body are very sharp. It is very agile and leaps all over the branches of trees.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Torchic
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has a flame sac inside its belly that perpetually burns. It feels warm if it is hugged.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Combusken
hoenn_pokedex.description: It boosts its concentration by emitting harsh cries. Its kicks have outstanding destructive power.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Blaziken
hoenn_pokedex.description: It can clear a 30-story building in a single leap. Its flaming punches scorch its foes.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Mudkip
hoenn_pokedex.description: The fin on its head acts as highly sensitive radar. It is able to navigate rivers without visibility.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Marshtomp
hoenn_pokedex.description: Its body is coated with a sticky fluid that helps it stay hydrated on land.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Swampert
hoenn_pokedex.description: It can swim while towing a large ship. It bashes down foes with arms that are like rock.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Poochyena
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has a very tenacious nature. It chases its prey until the victim becomes exhausted.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Mightyena
hoenn_pokedex.description: It will always obey the commands of a skilled Trainer. Its behavior arises from the days when it hunted in packs.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Zigzagoon
hoenn_pokedex.description: It walks in a zigzag fashion. It is good at finding items in the grass and even in the ground.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Linoone
hoenn_pokedex.description: When running in a straight line, it can easily top 60 miles per hour. It has a tough time with curved roads.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Wurmple
hoenn_pokedex.description: It lives amidst the tall grass and in forests. It repels attacks by raising up the spikes on its rear.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Silcoon
hoenn_pokedex.description: It drinks dew that collects on the silk covering its body. It is said that it hates the rain.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Beautifly
hoenn_pokedex.description: Its colorfully patterned wings are its most prominent feature. It sucks pollen with its long, thin mouth.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Cascoon
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is hot inside its cocoon. All the cells in its body are active in preparation for evolution.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Dustox
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is a nocturnal Pokémon that is attracted to the lights of cities. It scatters poisonous powder from its wings.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Lotad
hoenn_pokedex.description: It looks like an aquatic plant. It is said that it opens its leaf-like mouth to ferry Pokémon that can't swim.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Lombre
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is a mischievous Pokémon. It loves to tug on the lines of anglers and watch them panic.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Ludicolo with a Water Stone.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Ludicolo
hoenn_pokedex.description: When it hears festive music, all the cells in its body become stimulated, and it begins to dance.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Seedot
hoenn_pokedex.description: It hangs off branches and absorbs nutrients. When it becomes too heavy, it drops to the ground and rolls to a new location.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Nuzleaf
hoenn_pokedex.description: It lives in forests. It is said that when it blows the leaf on its head, it makes a sound like a flute.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Shiftry with a Leaf Stone.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Shiftry
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is a mysterious Pokémon that is said to live atop ancient trees. It can read its foe's thoughts.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Taillow
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has a gutsy spirit that makes it bravely take on tough foes. It flies in search of warm climates.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Swellow
hoenn_pokedex.description: It circles the skies in search of prey. Its shiny wings draw compliments from observers.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Wingull
hoenn_pokedex.description: It makes its nest on a sheer cliff at the edge of the sea. It has a habit of carrying prey in its beak.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Pelipper
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is a flying transporter that carries small Pokémon and eggs inside its massive bill.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Ralts
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is highly attuned to the emotions of people and Pokémon. It hides if it senses hostility.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Kirlia
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is said that a Kirlia that is exposed to the positive emotions of its Trainer grows beautiful.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Gardevoir or, if male, Gallade with a Dawn Stone.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Gardevoir
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has the power to predict the future. Its power peaks when it is protecting its Trainer.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Surskit
hoenn_pokedex.description: It appears as if it is skating on water. It draws sweet scents from the tip of its head to lure prey.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Masquerain
hoenn_pokedex.description: It intimidates enemies with the eye-like patterns on its antennae. It flaps its four wings to freely fly in any direction.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Shroomish
hoenn_pokedex.description: It loves to eat damp soil in forests. If you enter a forest after a long rain, you can see many Shroomish feasting on compost.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Breloom
hoenn_pokedex.description: It scatters poisonous spores and throws powerful punches while its foe is blinded.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Slakoth
hoenn_pokedex.description: It sleeps for 20 hours a day. It doesn't use much energy, so it needs to eat only a single leaf per day.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Vigoroth
hoenn_pokedex.description: It can't keep still because its blood boils with energy. It runs through the fields and mountains all day.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Slaking
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is the world's laziest Pokémon. It spends all day lying down and sleeping.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Nincada
hoenn_pokedex.description: It grows underground, absorbing nutrients from the roots of trees. It lives quietly.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Ninjask. Shedinja may appear if there is a spare Poké Ball and an empty party slot.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Ninjask
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is so fast that it is said to be able to evade any attack. It loves to eat sweet tree sap.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Shedinja
hoenn_pokedex.description: A discarded bug shell that came to life. Peering into the crack on its back is said to steal one's spirit.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Whismur
hoenn_pokedex.description: Its cries are whisper-quiet. If it senses danger, it lets out a cry as loud as a jet plane.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Loudred
hoenn_pokedex.description: It shouts loudly by inhaling and exhaling. It can knock a house down with its voice.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Exploud
hoenn_pokedex.description: Its bellowing is emitted from the holes on its body. It can be heard from six miles away.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Makuhita
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has a gutsy spirit. It will keep getting up no matter how many times it is knocked down.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Hariyama
hoenn_pokedex.description: It loves to match power with big-bodied Pokémon. It can knock a truck flying with its slaps.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Azurill
hoenn_pokedex.description: Its tail is packed full of the nutrients it needs to grow. It is constantly playing and bouncing on this tail.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Marill with high Happiness.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Nosepass
hoenn_pokedex.description: Its magnetic nose always points north. It is a helpful partner for Trainers who are traveling.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Probopass in a special magnetic field.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Skitty
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is said to be difficult to earn its trust. It is very cute when it chases its own tail.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Delcatty with a Moon Stone.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Delcatty
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is happy most of the time and doesn't fight. It prefers to nap in a comfortable spot.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Sableye
hoenn_pokedex.description: It feeds on gemstones. In darkness, its eyes sparkle with the glitter of jewels.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Mawile
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has two mouths. The big jaws on the back of its head can chew up iron beams.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Aron
hoenn_pokedex.description: It usually lives deep in mountains. It is a mystery as to why it appears in towns.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Lairon
hoenn_pokedex.description: It loves iron ore. It smashes its steely body against others in battles over territory.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Aggron
hoenn_pokedex.description: It claims a large mountain as its territory. It is incredibly proud of its horns.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Meditite
hoenn_pokedex.description: It never misses its daily yoga training. It is said that its mind and body are toughened by this training.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Medicham
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is said that through meditation, it has gained psychic powers. It can foresee its foe's moves.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Electrike
hoenn_pokedex.description: It stores electricity in its long body hair. It stimulates its leg muscles with electric charges.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Manectric
hoenn_pokedex.description: It discharges electricity from its mane. It creates thunderclouds and bolts of lightning.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Plusle
hoenn_pokedex.description: It cheers on its partners. It stores electricity in its body and shorts it out to create sparks.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Minun
hoenn_pokedex.description: It cheers on its partners. It absorbs electricity from telephone poles and shorts it out to create sparks.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Volbeat
hoenn_pokedex.description: It communicates with others by lighting up its tail. It loves the sweet scent of Illumise.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Illumise
hoenn_pokedex.description: It guides Volbeat to draw signs in the night sky. There are more than 200 different designs.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Roselia
hoenn_pokedex.description: The flowers on its arms are fragrant. It gives off a relaxing fragrance that calms people.
hoenn_pokedex.evolution: Evolves into Roserade with a Shiny Stone.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Gulpin
hoenn_pokedex.description: It has a stomach that could digest scrap iron. It swallows anything that is smaller than itself.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Swalot
hoenn_pokedex.description: It can swallow a tire whole in one gulp. It secretes a horribly toxic fluid from the pores on its body.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Carvanha
hoenn_pokedex.description: They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls.

hoenn_pokedex.name: Sharpedo
hoenn_pokedex.description: It is the bully of the sea. Its fangs rip through iron sheets. It can swim at 75 mph.
